descript.abstract: Election Districts and Precincts in Frederick County
descript.purpose: To depict the boundaries of election districts and precincts in Frederick County

idinfo.accconst: Employees of Frederick County, Maryland may access this data. Governmental agencies and private groups or individuals performing contract work for Frederick County may also be provided access to the data by the County's Enterprise GIS Manager.
idinfo.useconst: Frederick County employees have unrestricted use of the data, but are not permitted to distribute the data in its raw format to external groups or individuals without consent from the Enterprise GIS Manager. For governmental agencies and private groups or individuals provided with the data, use is in accordance with Frederick County, Maryland's GIS License Agreement. While efforts have been made to ensure the accuracy of the data, Frederick County accepts no responsibility for errors, omissions, or positional inaccuracies in the data. Frederick County makes no warranty, express or implied, and disclaims all implied warranties of merchantability, integration, title, and fitness of the GIS data for a particular purpose. Reliance on the data is at the risk of the user.
